s and discuss open questions in\nour approach.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 23 Dec 2005 16:17:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 25 Jan 2007 19:42:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2010-10-27"}
