ysics case together with possible scenarios for the high\nluminosity SuperB Factory based on the concepts of the Linear Collider and the\nrelated experimental issues are discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 23 Dec 2005 20:54:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
